# COMPUTER SCIENCE puzzles (prefix: CS_) 

CS_ROOM1_NAME = Classroom 101
CS_ROOM1_PUZZLE = What subject uses variables, loops, and functions?
CS_ROOM1_ANSWER = Programming
CS_ROOM1_CLUE = Think about what you do in CS class every day.
CS_ROOM1_HINT = It starts with the letter P.

CS_ROOM2_NAME = Library
CS_ROOM2_PUZZLE = FIFO data structure used in scheduling and buffering?
CS_ROOM2_ANSWER = Queue
CS_ROOM2_CLUE = Think about people waiting in line for something.
CS_ROOM2_HINT = First to enter is the first to leave.

CS_ROOM3_NAME = TSG
CS_ROOM3_PUZZLE = Convert binary 10110 to decimal.
CS_ROOM3_ANSWER = 22
CS_ROOM3_CLUE = Add values of 1 bit using powers of 2
CS_ROOM3_HINT = Add 16 + 4 + 2

CS_ROOM4_NAME = Security Office
CS_ROOM4_PUZZLE = What OOP principle allows us to create new classes based on existing ones?
CS_ROOM4_ANSWER = Inheritance
CS_ROOM4_CLUE = Think of a child getting traits from their parents.
CS_ROOM4_HINT = It starts with the letter I.

# ── NURSING puzzles (prefix: NR_)

NR_ROOM1_NAME = Classroom 101
NR_ROOM1_PUZZLE = What do nurses measure to check how fast the heart is beating?
NR_ROOM1_ANSWER = pulse
NR_ROOM1_CLUE = You can feel it on the wrist or the neck.
NR_ROOM1_HINT = It starts with the letter P.

NR_ROOM2_NAME = Library
NR_ROOM2_PUZZLE = What is the normal human body temperature in Celsius?
NR_ROOM2_ANSWER = 37
NR_ROOM2_CLUE = It is the standard temperature a nurse checks with a thermometer.
NR_ROOM2_HINT = It is a two-digit number between 36 and 38.

NR_ROOM3_NAME = TSG
NR_ROOM3_PUZZLE = What do nurses use to record and access patient medical information digitally?
NR_ROOM3_ANSWER = EMR
NR_ROOM3_CLUE = TSG manages the hospital software system nurses use every day.
NR_ROOM3_HINT = Three letters. Stands for Electronic Medical Records.

NR_ROOM4_NAME = Security Office
NR_ROOM4_PUZZLE = What is the name of the oath nurses take, named after a famous nurse?
NR_ROOM4_ANSWER = nightingale pledge
NR_ROOM4_CLUE = Named after the founder of modern nursing.
NR_ROOM4_HINT = Two words. Think of Florence __________.